     ============================================================================================== -->
<section id="about" class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row-layout">
            <div class="col-text fade-left">
                <h4 class="section-tag">About Egypt</h4>
                <h2 class="section-title">Where History Comes Alive</h2>
                <p class="section-desc">
                    Egypt is not just a country; it is a timeline of human civilization. From the dawn of time, the Nile River has nourished a culture that built the impossible. The ancient Egyptians gifted the world with mathematics, medicine, agriculture, and architecture that still baffles modern engineers.
                </p>
                <p class="section-desc">
                    Today, Egypt represents a unique fusion. You can stand before the Great Sphinx in the morning, haggle for spices in a medieval bazaar at noon, and dive into the vibrant coral reefs of the Red Sea by sunset. It is a land of contrasts, mystery, and unparalleled hospitality.
                </p>
                <p class="section-desc">
                    Whether you are walking through the chaotic, energetic streets of Cairo or floating silently on a Felucca in Aswan, the energy of Egypt is palpable. It is a destination that changes you, offering a perspective on time and humanity found nowhere else on Earth.
                </p>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Home to the Great Pyramid, the only remaining Wonder of the Ancient World.</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Over 2,000km of pristine coastline on the Mediterranean and Red Sea.</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> A culinary journey of flavors blending Middle Eastern, African, and Mediterranean influences.</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> World-class museums including the Grand Egyptian Museum (GEM).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-image fade-right">
                <div class="image-stack">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1572252009286-268acec5ca0a?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Sphinx" class="img-back">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568322445389-f64ac2515020?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Temple" class="img-front">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

